casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Ashburn, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Ashburn (1997), 78 Ohio St.3d 1221.]

(No. 96-1585 Submitted April 1, 1997 Decided May 14, 1997.) David A. Hackenberg, Director of Law, and Robert A. Beutler, Jr., Assistant Director of Law, for appellee. Steven D. Christopher, for appellant.

The appeal is dismissed, sum sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
